<p class="indent2" style="-uslm-lc:I13" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">In the case of loss years beginning before <date date="1987-01-01">January 1, 1987</date>, the amount of the net operating loss which may be carried over to taxable years beginning after <date date="1986-12-31">December 31, 1986</date>, for purposes of paragraph (2), shall be equal to the amount which may be carried from the loss year to the first taxable year of the taxpayer beginning after <date date="1986-12-31">December 31, 1986</date>.</p>
